    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一位老朋友在《新威尔斯之罪》中回归。这段故事发生在全新的区域，但一切和从前并没有什么两样……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>罪孽吞噬的城市</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >罪人、毒品、谋杀和记者在新威尔斯横行。调查谋杀案的警探罗伊·萨姆森被调到第九区，负责揭露城市地下网络的腐败。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333870/extras/b4ca5f9fe6d6f6466a9d3f9bbe92b14b.poster.avif?t=1758882347\" width=780 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333870/extras/b4ca5f9fe6d6f6466a9d3f9bbe92b14b.webm?t=1758882347\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>四个可调查的新情节</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跟随罗伊·萨姆森和他的新搭档克里夫·萨维亚，参与调查四项全新案件，解决一个使新威尔斯乌烟瘴气的犯罪集团组织。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>致命追捕</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但事情没有看上去那么简单，发生了一些史无前例的情况。雷姆利亚魔法再次占据了头条。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333870/extras/d4c409f1741f483446d2ce1861fc49e4.poster.avif?t=1758882347\" width=780 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333870/extras/d4c409f1741f483446d2ce1861fc49e4.webm?t=1758882347\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>调查新老角色</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >运用你的侦探技巧审问语焉不详的证人，拼凑谋杀线索并读懂言外之意来揭露真相。</p>",
